<h2 id="toc5"><span>Teletype backgrounds</span></h2>
<p>Adds a light grey background to &lt;tt&gt; elements (<tt><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">{{text}}</span></tt>).</p>
<div class="code">
<div class="hl-main">
<pre>
